    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>You cause a targeted object to unlock, unstick, or unbar itself.</em></p><p>Choose an object that you can see within range. The object can be a door, a box, a chest, a set of manacles, a padlock, or another object that contains a mundane or magical means that prevents access. A target that is held shut by a mundane lock or that is stuck or barred becomes unlocked, unstuck, or unbarred.</p><p>If the object has multiple locks, only one of them is unlocked. If you choose a target that is held shut with <em>arcane lock</em>, that spell is suppressed for 10 minutes, during which time the target can be opened and shut normally.</p><p>When you cast the spell, a loud knock, audible from as far away as 300 feet, emanates from the target object.</p>",
      "source": {
        "fallback": "Black Flag Reference Document"
      },
      "short": "Open a locked object."
